data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Newberry Place! This exceptionally spacious residence boasts an impressive 4,040 square feet of heated and cooled living space, offering a perfect blend of space and comfort. With 6 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, an office/den, a loft/family room, and interior laundry room, this home is designed to accommodate your every need.    As you step inside, you are greeted by the den, followed by a traditionally styled dining room that sets the tone for elegant gatherings. The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a convenient eat-in space for casual meals. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the expansive living room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.    The primary bedroom is a retreat within itself, boasting a tray ceiling, a spacious walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom that exudes luxury. The bathroom is equipped with split vanities, a soaking tub, and a walk-in shower, providing the perfect oasis to unwind after a long day.    Entertain friends and family on the large covered and screened back lanai, overlooking the fully fenced backyard – a private haven for outdoor enjoyment. With a 3-car garage, there's ample space for your vehicles and storage needs.    Beyond the enchanting features of this home, Newberry Place offers a family-friendly environment with amenities such as a kids' playground and athletic courts. The community is situated in the ever-growing city of Newberry, known for its enriched history, local dining, parks, reputable schools, and a plethora of activities. Just a short 10-minute drive away, you'll find the vibrant Tioga Town Center, and a quick 15-minute drive takes you to the bustling city of Gainesville.    Don't miss this opportunity to make Newberry Place your home, where luxury, convenience, and community converge seamlessly. Schedule your showing today and step into a life of comfort and style!
